snippet.title: Bold Moves+ | Match 3 Word Puzzle Game Available Now on Apple Arcade
snippet.description:
Bold Moves+ in now available on Apple Arcade, elevating the match 3 game experience with messages of positivity and personal growth. Download and play free now: http://apple.co/boldmoves_ 

Get your daily dose of positivity with Bold Moves+, the positively relaxing (and challenging) match 3 word puzzle game. Match 3 colors to collect letter tiles, break through obstacles, and solve the phrase to find inspiration from motivational quotes and positive affirmations. Earn rewards and boosters, progress through chapters of puzzles, and win limited-time events. Take some time to unwind with serene scenes, challenging levels, weekly events, and inspiring puzzles.


Download Bold Moves+ on Apple Arcade for iPhone and iPad: http://apple.co/boldmoves_ 
Subscribe to Apple Arcade for $4.99/month with a one-month free trial. Apple Arcade is part of Apple One’s Individual ($16.95), Family ($22.95), and Premier ($32.95) monthly plans, with a one-month free trial.
